## Nginx: space-separated domains for server_name
## Examples:
## LARAVEL_SERVER_NAMES="laravel.local.com laravel.test"
## NEST_SERVER_NAMES="nest.local.com nest.test"
## REACT_SERVER_NAMES="react.local.com react.test"
LARAVEL_SERVER_NAMES=laravel.local.com
NEST_SERVER_NAMES=nest.local.com
REACT_SERVER_NAMES=react.local.com